# Build context for flasher/Dockerfile (context root is the repo root). Without
# this the context would be the whole repo (kernel/, archive/, .git - many GB).
# Keep only the flasher sources and the mlflash binary the image embeds.
*
!flasher
!native
native/*
!native/build
native/build/*
!native/build/mlflash

# Artifacts the image rebuilds itself.
flasher/build
flasher/internal/payload/mlflash
